I think it all comes down to why you play a Paladin. If your into it because you wanted to do mad amounts of damage… your playing the wrong class. If your into because a Paladin most closely conforms to your ideals of the game… your playing the right class! I play a Paladin because I like to and it just seems “right” to me. I have never had problems finding a group. That’s why I joined a Guild. Basically if you are upset about the lacking of the Paladin class then perhaps you are playing the wrong class. I for one could not imagine playing any other class.<br>
