<br>
Additionally, if you cant seem to get in a group, get your ass out there and make a group...hell I have done that before.<br>
<br>
Seems people in the high end game are not all retards from ebay or impateint, some like to just kill stuff and have fun with people they know.<br>
<br>
My class isn't broken and neither are pally's, I dont care who can hit for more sustained damage, and I dont have problems getting in groups unless hell, all the freaking spots are camped and there just arent any more places for ANYONE like Seb in prime time.   Show of hands for this:  In a group, good group, /ooc camp check, reply &quot;EVERYTHING - NOW SHUT UP&quot;...I say more places to hunt, that will help - world is getting crowded.<br>
<br>
For every group out there that will not take you, there are plenty of people who are LFG as well...I would take a 3 pally group any day for the tanks - its a group...it might go a little slower (might not), but the rat race to 60 just isnt what I have in mind, I can solo if that was what I wanted - but what a boring life that is.   If you get a person who doesnt want to group with you because they have a masters in mathmatics and are constantly looking at thier exp bar and watch, well screw em-let them group with all the other impatient players...they have alot in common and so do the people like you.<br>
